{"tid":2026894,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(氣氛詭異)  中共兩會開議  白晝卻漆黑一片","createTime":"2020-05-21T08:44:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-21T16:49:51.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6ff37eb932144c9a078c0297acb3793fefd5fb86","tid":2026894,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T08:44:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2020/05/21/realtime/7913021.png&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=800&amp;exp=3600&amp;w=930&amp;nt=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2020%2F05%2F21%2Frealtime%2F7913021.png%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D800%26exp%3D3600%26w%3D930%26nt%3D1&h=a11fd2b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中共一年一度的兩會終於在五月二十一日開議。今天下午三點上場的是中共全國第十三屆三次代表大會，可是北京的天空十分不尋常，明明是白晝，卻漆黑一片，宛如黑夜。這是歷屆兩會中罕見的天候現象。<br />\n<br />\n中共兩會的天氣，一向是中共官媒做文章的話題之一。2018年兩會期間，降了一場小雪，那是前一年冬季以來唯一的一次降雪。一陸眾多官媒曾經大肆報導「天降瑞雪」，是祥瑞之兆，慶祝兩會成功。據新浪微博網友後來發現，那是由於大陸氣象部門在北京郊區發射雨彈，增加了降雪的機會。<br />\n<br />\n2018年的中共全國兩會，「天降瑞雪」和上海第一財經女記者在代表通道記者會上猛翻白眼，是那年大陸微博微信網友討論度最多的議題。<br />\n<br />\n中共中央氣象局的官方預報是，今天有降雨天氣，主要影響為午後至傍晚，外出必須攜帶雨具，注意交通安全。二十一日白天陰，上午有小雨或零星小雨，午後至傍晚有雷陣雨，北轉南風二三級，最高氣溫攝氏二十二度。<br />\n<br />\n稍早，中共全國政協會議開議時，全體委員、官員，曾對中國大陸新冠肺炎中去世的民眾默哀一分鐘。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2020/05/21/realtime/7913022.png&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=800&amp;exp=3600&amp;w=800&amp;nt=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2020%2F05%2F21%2Frealtime%2F7913022.png%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D800%26exp%3D3600%26w%3D800%26nt%3D1&h=54efa6c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/7331/4580530\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F7331%2F4580530&d=JWMo9xAWlgSpyjxIujWPsWCvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=bed5b4ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/7331/4580530</a>"},{"pid":"5185b79d28ac30cd3c36bf80636797a93608ccf0","tid":2026894,"uid":62802,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T08:46:05.000Z","msg":"求幫推<br />\n[香港文化] 上連登打正字<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2026832\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2026832</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0d1c964eb36ffbe3c65f6aa2703695327c42dd4a","tid":2026894,"uid":270798,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T08:46:12.000Z","msg":"有消息話北京兩會期間, 全北京斷網, 唔知真唔真 ?"},{"pid":"482bd0abd126f0e830253b7ad4ec02528dafce7d","tid":2026894,"uid":78873,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T08:46:18.000Z","msg":"你睇魔戒 魔多會唔會光到白天咁？"},{"pid":"2eb91a9a90955c86cede1d01a6a0cec76d6a92ef","tid":2026894,"uid":123848,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T08:54:59.000Z","msg":"好快玩完"},{"pid":"e50b2331cbe33c9cabf6b5978780d9ca4f370fd5","tid":2026894,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T16:15:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/41.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aed401b0f8efaeb796679836facd9cdade1a7cde","tid":2026894,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T16:31:26.000Z","msg":"召喚左神龍氏？"},{"pid":"77569ccdf609163a68d50672a42d039a42f56b8e","tid":2026894,"uid":9564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d1c964eb36ffbe3c65f6aa2703695327c42dd4a","tid":2026894,"uid":270798,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T08:46:12.000Z","msg":"有消息話北京兩會期間, 全北京斷網, 唔知真唔真 ?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T16:32:47.000Z","msg":"唔係啦<br />\n有朋友北京啲人係咁send相俾佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fc27dff5e04d9d82841ca7836e9ee1a97f882e6","tid":2026894,"uid":13281,"like":